## HARDWARE WIRING (XIAO ESP32S3 Sense + SD Module)

### Microphone (Built-in PDM — NO wiring needed)
The XIAO ESP32S3 Sense has a built-in MSM261D3526H1CPM PDM mic.
Firmware uses:  DATA→GPIO42   CLK→GPIO41

### SD Card (external SPI module or XIAO Expansion Board)
SD Module Pin   →  XIAO ESP32S3 Pin
──────────────────────────────────
MOSI            →  GPIO9  (D9)
MISO            →  GPIO8  (D8)
SCK             →  GPIO7  (D7)
CS              →  GPIO4  (D4)   ← change SD_CS in .ino if different
VCC             →  3.3V
GND             →  GND

⚠️ FORMAT SD CARD AS FAT32 before first use.
⚠️ Max recommended card size: 32GB

### LED (Built-in — NO wiring needed)
Firmware uses GPIO21 (LED_BUILTIN on XIAO ESP32S3).

