## MAC PYTHON SETUP

### 1. Install dependencies (run once)
pip3 install bleak openai-whisper gspread oauth2client \
             rapidfuzz word2number --break-system-packages

brew install ffmpeg   # required by whisper

### 2. Google Sheets credentials
Place your credentials.json in the same folder as vaani_mac_receiver.py
(Same credentials.json from your existing server.py setup)

### 3. Run receiver
cd vaani_mac_receiver_folder/
python3 vaani_mac_receiver.py

The script will:
  - Scan BLE every 10 seconds
  - Auto-connect when XIAO is in range
  - Download all queued WAV files
  - Run Whisper on each file
  - Update Google Sheets inventory

